      <p>Recent comparable sales in your area show strong market activity. Properties similar to yours have sold at competitive prices, indicating healthy buyer demand in your neighborhood.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="analysis-stats">
      <div class="analysis-stat"><div class="num">{{ stats.total_comps | default(4) }}</div><div class="lbl">Comps</div></div>
